text: Bulpitt is a village in Illinois in the United States. According to the 2020 census, there were 212 residents. 22.0% of the village's population was under the age of 18, 19.5% was between the ages of 18 and 24, 25.9% was between the ages of 25 and 44, 22.4% was between the ages of 45 and 64, and 10.2% was 65 or older. 28.0 years old was the median age. There were 95.0 men for every 100 females. There were 76.9 males for every 100 females aged 18 and older. Category:Villages in Illinois
title: Bulpitt, Illinois
